ZH: 猪是一种很可爱的动物。
EN: Pigs are very cute animals.

ZH: 这只猪有个粉红色的鼻子。
EN: This pig has a pink nose.

ZH: 现在农场里有一只大胖猪。
EN: There is a big fat pig in the farm now.

ZH: 猪是中国十二生肖之一。
EN: Pigs are one of the twelve zodiac animals in China.

ZH: 我喜欢吃猪肉汉堡。
EN: I like to eat pork burgers.

ZH: 这只猪很懒，整天只知道睡觉。
EN: This pig is very lazy, it sleeps all day.

ZH: 猪在田地里找吃的。
EN: Pigs are looking for food in the field.

ZH: 这只小猪很聪明，会做很多小把戏。
EN: This little pig is very smart, it can do many tricks.

ZH: 猪在猫和狗之后是第三聪明的动物。
EN: Pigs are the third smartest animals after cats and dogs.

ZH: 猪是综艺节目《猪猪侠》中的形象。
EN: Pigs are characters in the variety show "Pigman".

ZH: 这只猪是我的宠物，名叫小花。
EN: This pig is my pet, its name is Xiaohua.

ZH: 猪可以吃很多不同的食物。
EN: Pigs can eat a variety of food.

ZH: 农场里的猪都很健康。
EN: The pigs on the farm are all healthy.

ZH: 猪很擅长在泥浆中打滚。
EN: Pigs are good at rolling in the mud.

ZH: 这只猪迷路了，我们得帮助它找回家。
EN: This pig is lost, we need to help it find its way home.

ZH: 猪可以给我们提供很多有用的产品，如肉和皮。
EN: Pigs can provide us with many useful products, such as meat and leather.

ZH: 猪的叫声很大，特别是在饿的时候。
EN: Pigs make a loud noise, especially when they are hungry.

ZH: 猪智商很高，可以识别自己的名字。
EN: Pigs are intelligent and can recognize their own names.

ZH: 这只猪被称为农场的老大。
EN: This pig is known as the leader of the farm.

ZH: 猪是一个值得我们尊重和保护的物种。
EN: Pigs are a species worthy of our respect and protection.
